%T1528.LOM.Description%             = T1528,     PCI\VEN_8086&DEV_1528&SUBSYS_00D41137
%T1528.Dual.EM.Description%         = T1528,     PCI\VEN_8086&DEV_1528&SUBSYS_7B14108E
