%T1528.Copper.ECNA.Description%     = T1528_PM,  PCI\VEN_8086&DEV_1528&SUBSYS_04718086
%T1528.Copper.FLEXLOM.Description%  = T1528_PM,  PCI\VEN_8086&DEV_1528&SUBSYS_107317AA
